title: Classic Canadian Rock - 2013 - cdrip [flac]
description:
Classic Canadian Rock - 2013 - cdrip - flac

A very tasty set of classic Canadian rock hits; a sampler of other bands for those whose knowledge of Canadian rock music doesn't go any farther than the Guess Who and Neil Young.

01 Mama Let Him Play - Doucette
02 Paradise - Max Webster featuring Kim Mitchell
03 Fly At Night - Chilliwack
04 Closer To The Heart - Rush
05 Something to Live For - Barney Bentall and the Legendary Hearts
06 If I Had A Rocket Launcher - Bruce Cockburn
07 A Criminal Mind - Gowan
08 You're Daddy Don't Know - Toronto
09 Monkey Bars - Coney Hatch
10 Don't It Make Ya Feel - Headpins
